OL,3,CUse randomly selected 'citizens
OL,4,Cpanels' to help fight populism, says
OL,5,Cthink tank
OL,7,FRandomly selected "citizens panels"
OL,8,Fshould help set Government policy in
OL,9,Forder to combat populism and
OL,10,Fdisillusionment with politics, a think
OL,11,Ftank has said.
OL,13,FIn a report published on Monday, cross-
OL,14,Fparty think tank Demos urged the
OL,15,FGovernment to "embark on a new era of
OL,16,Fpublic participation in policy making"
OL,17,Fas a way of restoring trust in
OL,18,Fpolitics.
