OL,4,Cpanels' to help fight populism, says
OL,5,Cthink tank
OL,7,FMiriam Levin, one of the report's
OL,8,Fauthors, said: "Our political system
OL,9,Fisn't equipped to deal with the scale
OL,10,Fof the challenges we face, nor the
OL,11,Flooming threat of populism.
OL,13,F"We need a new layer of participation
OL,14,Fembedded at the heart of our political
OL,15,Fsystem to renew our democracy."
