OL,5,Cthink tank
OL,7,FMs Levin pointed to declining
OL,8,Fengagement in politics, illustrated by
OL,9,Fturnout in this year's election
OL,10,Ffalling to 59.9% ` the lowest since
OL,11,F2001 and the third lowest since the
OL,12,Fintroduction of universal suffrage in
OL,13,F1918 ` as evidence of the need for
OL,14,Fgreater public involvement.
OL,16,FShe said: "The Prime Minister has
OL,17,Frightly identified this as a
OL,18,Fpremiership-defining test. Our
OL,19,FCitizens' White Paper sets out clearly
OL,20,Fhow and why participation should be at
OL,21,Fthe heart of his government's efforts.
