OL,5,Cthink tank
OL,7,F"Involving citizens in the decisions
OL,8,Fthat affect their lives is not only a
OL,9,Fproven and effective way of navigating
OL,10,Fthe trade-offs that have historically
OL,11,Fprevented meaningful progress being
OL,12,Fmade on complex issues such as social
OL,13,Fcare reform, it's also popular among
OL,14,Fthe general public."
