OL,5,Cthink tank
OL,7,FAmong the proposals in the Demos
OL,8,Freport is the creation of "citizens
OL,9,Fpanels", made up of randomly selected,
OL,10,Fdemographically representative
OL,11,Findividuals to feed into the "mission
OL,12,Fboards" that will oversee delivery of
OL,13,Fthe Government's top priorities.
OL,15,FThe report also called for greater use
OL,16,Fof "citizens assemblies" to solve
OL,17,Fpolitically thorny issues such as
OL,18,Fsocial care, and to debate "moral
OL,19,Fquestions" such as assisted dying.
