OL,4,Cpanels' to help fight populism, says
OL,5,Cthink tank
OL,7,FThese bodies, generally selected at
OL,8,Frandom in a way similar to juries, are
OL,9,Ftasked with deliberating on these
OL,10,Fissues and coming up with proposals
OL,11,Fafter receiving expert evidence.
OL,13,FSome Labour figures have previously
OL,14,Fexpressed support for the idea of
OL,15,Fcitizens assemblies, with the Prime
OL,16,FMinister's chief of staff, Sue Grey,
OL,17,Fknown to be in favour of them.
