OL,5,Cthink tank
OL,7,FCitizens assemblies have also been
OL,8,Fused in Ireland to produce proposals
OL,9,Fon a range of areas including
OL,10,Flegalising abortion and gender
OL,11,Fequality.
OL,13,FThe proposals on abortion were
OL,14,Fapproved by a referendum, but others
OL,15,Fhave been defeated when put to the
OL,16,Fwider public, leading some to question
OL,17,Fthe effectiveness of citizens
OL,18,Fassemblies.
